{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcsSuuSB4iNP4sCUzQ5ba","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I found the real constraint: RabbitMQ only supports mixed-version clustering between **adjacent** minor releases — jumping straight to 3.13 broke clustering with the still-3.9 nodes (feature-flag RPC incompatibility). Also, I realized StatefulSet template image changes force full Pod recreation (wiping the emptyDir data), whereas patching a running Pod's `spec.containers[0].image` directly triggers an in-place container restart that **preserves the emptyDir volume** — the correct way to upgrade a stateful RabbitMQ node without relying on cross-node mirroring for every hop. Let me first repair rabbitmq-2 back to 3.9 and rejoin it properly."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":296,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1632,"cache_read_input_tokens":130014,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1632},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3fb2359b-9b20-4640-bc08-db4382155585","uuid":"338f45b6-4fb4-4aa1-b28b-74614c71484d","request_id":"req_011CcsSut9Y772Ka4eMuixxn"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcsSuuSB4iNP4sCUzQ5ba","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01XRNEqYqgNnT9v5HBUc6vss","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"NS=karma-rabbitmq-skip-upgrade-3-9-to-4-e48ae613-cluster-a\necho \"--- set partition high so STS controller never touches existing pods ---\"\nkubectl -n $NS patch statefulset rabbitmq --type=merge -p '{\"spec\":{\"updateStrategy\":{\"rollingUpdate\":{\"partition\":3}}}}'\necho \"--- revert STS template image to 3.9 for bookkeeping consistency ---\"\nkubectl -n $NS patch statefulset rabbitmq --type=json -p '[{\"op\":\"replace\",\"path\":\"/spec/template/spec/containers/0/image\",\"value\":\"rabbitmq:3.9-management\"}]'\necho \"--- patch rabbitmq-2 pod image in place back to 3.9 ---\"\nkubectl -n $NS patch pod rabbitmq-2 --type=json -p '[{\"op\":\"replace\",\"path\":\"/spec/containers/0/image\",\"value\":\"rabbitmq:3.9-management\"}]'\nkubectl -n $NS get pods -l app=rabbitmq -o jsonpath='{range .items[*]}{.metadata.name}{\"\\t\"}{.spec.containers[0].image}{\"\\n\"}{end}'\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":296,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1632,"cache_read_input_tokens":130014,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1632},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"3fb2359b-9b20-4640-bc08-db4382155585","uuid":"ba9b9387-4e82-426d-9cae-d6f230db13d2","request_id":"req_011CcsSut9Y772Ka4eMuixxn"}
